@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001
@conversationId = {{createConversation.response.body.id}}

### 🟢 Create new conversation
# @name createConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/conversations
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 🟢 Send a message to the conversation
# @name sendMessage
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/conversations/{{conversationId}}/messages
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

"Tell me a joke about agents and databases."

###

### List all conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/conversations
Accept: application/json

###

### Get details of one conversation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/conversations/{{conversationId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Stream a conversation (Server-Sent Events)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/conversations/{{conversationId}}/stream
Accept: text/event-stream
Content-Type: application/json

"Write a haiku about persistence."
